div.span: Corda CA's used in day-to-day use. The network map cert is used to sign the network parameters which change with each version and when a new node is added. The doorman CA is used to issue node certificates to vendors.

div.div: Notary certificates are only issued to notaries. The test network has a central notary and the production network will feature a set of notaries hosted by vendors.
